<![CDATA[ Which are the best values that any Software Engineer should have? ]]>
</title>
<link>https://medium.com/@gabriel_avila/which-are-the-best-values-that-any-software-engineer-should-have-12a312a9a411?source=rss-e2a7c82d399b------2</link>
